m2mimud.game
Class FriendsList

java.lang.Object
  m2mimud.game.FriendsList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
public class FriendsList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Externalizable

The friends' list is an object which stores information about a player's friends. It notifes them when they join the session they are in, and when they leave a session. Its main purpose is to help players distinguish between the various characters who have the same name.
